  "body": " /kind bug\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n**What happened**:\r\ncrdStorageMap read write in `removeDeadStorage`\r\nhttps://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/master/staging/src/k8s.io/apiextensions-apiserver/pkg/apiserver/customresource_handler.go#L268\r\n\r\nand \r\n`updateCustomResourceDefinition `\r\nhttps://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/master/staging/src/k8s.io/apiextensions-apiserver/pkg/apiserver/customresource_handler.go#L448~#L453\r\n\r\nhave data race when multiple threads run it. Because in `removeDeadStorage` the operate on `crdStorageMap ` is without lock.\r\n\r\n",
